<title>Show or Hide the Ruler</title>
<context ID_VIEW_RULER />

<subheader>To show or hide line and column numbers ...</subheader>

Click <image ruler_button.png /> on the toolbar; or from the <b>View</b> menu, select <b>Ruler</b>; or press <b>Ctrl+R</b>. A check mark appears next to the <b>Ruler</b> menu item when the line and column numbers are displayed.

The ruler is shown for all files. Text Viewer remembers this setting between runs.

<seealso select_text.hgt />
